release_note: Apple Pencil users can get ready for 2024 with Penbook s new Mind and Body notebook series. Track habits plan goals and sketch your ambitions on dynamic Live Paper that includes your calendar events and fits your device perfectly.

Apple Pencil users can now create custom notebooks with dated journal sections mixed stationery and title pages. Best of all you can share your custom notebook layouts anywhere. Tap the Create tab in the app to learn more. This minor update fixes a bug with page zoom and alignment.

Apple Pencil users this one s for you: Penbook 6 now keeps your ink sharp no matter how far you zoom in. Try the new double tap gesture on the writing canvas to see it in action. You ll also love the new pagination that lets you peek at your next and previous pages for easy reference. This minor update fixes ink misaligning with the paper at certain zoom levels.

Apple Pencil fans can now opt in to get notified about notebook suggestions. We also improved the Editions previews and increased the responsiveness of the writing page.
Apple Pencil users who were missing our old patterned notebook covers will be happy to see them added back they re in the Texture section with a bunch of new patterns too .

Apple Pencil users can now backup and restore their entire notebook libraries. Exporting PDFs is also much more reliable. This minor update fixes a bug where the toolbar was showing up in the wrong color. Sorry!
Apple Pencil users will love the new bullet journal inspired notebook. We ve also added an option in the tablature stationeries for ukulele tabs.
Apple Pencil users: this minor update fixes a progress bar seriously . It also includes some behind the scenes performance fixes to prepare for our next major release.

Apple Pencil users this is a big one PDF Import! Just like you asked for. Import PDFs mark them up rearrange pages and add notes. Maps! You can create stylized maps and stick them into your notes. Perfect for bullet journals and travel planning. Tag your books! Like folders but better. Better search! Not overselling it. It can read your cursive yes even yours. Now it searches all your books at once. Left handed layout! Sorry it took us so long. Swipe on the top menu to swing it to the left or right side of the device or hide it away. New cover styles! I made them myself. New book maker! Make your perfect day planner or study book in just a few taps. This minor update fixes a layout issue in the onboarding and account areas.

Apple Pencil users meet your new favorite accessory: the scratchpad. It s a long long strip of paper right next to your notebook and it keeps memos drawings and anything else you want to reuse or remember next to all of your pages and books. You can access it from the new button in the drawing toolbar or by swiping from the right edge of your device.
